 (22,'MENU_ITEM',500,700,'YES','Guides and Brownies','','<br />\r\n<h2>Guides and Brownies</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Guides</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n  <A href=\"http://www.girlguiding.org.uk\">Guides Website</A>\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n  What is guiding?\r\n\r\n\r\n  Guiding is a game - with a purpose. It provides opportunities for girls and             young women to be challenged by new adventures and experiences and achieve a sense of pride in accomplishment and teaches them to understand and learn about the world, its people and cultures. \r\n </p>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n    Contact\r\n    <p>\r\n      Ann Holbeach\r\n      <br />\r\n      27 Grayling Road,\r\n      <br />\r\n      Stambermill.\r\n      <br />\r\n\r\n      Ann Holbeach\r\n\r\n<form action=\"index.php?displaypage=mailform.php\" method=\"post\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"emailrecipient\" \r\nvalue=\"ann.holbeach@christchurchlye.org.uk\">\r\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Email Ann\">\r\n</form>\r\n\r\n    </p>\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!---------------------------------- -->\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<h2>Brownies</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n  <A href=\"http://www.girlguiding.org.uk/brownies/\">Brownies Website</A>\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n <p>\r\n  Being a Brownie is all about having loads of fun and a huge adventure! To be a       Brownie you have just got to be a girl aged between seven and 10 years old.\r\n\r\nBrownies meet together in a Pack most weeks. The Pack is made up of small groups called Sixes. A Six is a fab group of friends that has a great time together. You have a special badge to show what Six you belong to.\r\n\r\nThe Pack is run by a Guider and a team of adult leaders. They look after you and make sure you have a great time on your Brownie Adventure.\r\n  </P>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n  Contact\r\n  <br />\r\n  <br />\r\n  Rose Chambers\r\n  <br />\r\n  01384 - 894365\r\n  <br />\r\n\r\n  Rose Chambers\r\n\r\n<form action=\"index.php?displaypage=mailform.php\" method=\"post\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" nam