 (61,'MENU_ITEM',500,200,'YES','Net Cafe','','<br />\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>\r\n  Net Cafe \r\n</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe Net Cafe is a place for the community to come and enjoy a warm and welcoming atmosphere and somewhere to bring or meet new friends. You can just use the Net Cafe to browse the web, send or receive e-mails, work or shop.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id=\"slideshow\" style=\"float:left; padding:1em;\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"active\">\r\n        <img src=\"jpgs/slide/netcafe/netcafe003.jpg\" alt=\"Slideshow Image 5\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div>\r\n        <img src=\"jpgs/slide/netcafe/netcafe004.jpg\" alt=\"Slideshow Image 6\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div>\r\n        <img src=\"jpgs/slide/netcafe/netcafe006.jpg\" alt=\"Slideshow Image 2\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div>\r\n        <img src=\"jpgs/slide/netcafe/netcafe001.jpg\" alt=\"Slideshow Image 3\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div>\r\n        <img src=\"jpgs/slide/netcafe/netcafe002.jpg\" alt=\"Slideshow Image 4\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<b>Opening Times</b>\r\n<p>\r\nTuesday 10:30am - 5:00pm\r\n<br />\r\nThursday 10:30am - 4:00pm\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>On Sale</b>\r\n<p>\r\nCakes, Baguettes, Soft Drinks, Tea, Coffee, Espresso, Cappuccino,\r\nMocha, Latte, Hot Chocolate & More\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Activities</b>\r\n<p>\r\nAs well as the opportunity to learn how to use the web better, we are also hoping to offer Arts and Crafts workshops from time to time.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"clear:left;\">\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<b>DMBC Library Service</b>\r\n<p>\r\nDon\'t forget that \r\n<a href=\"http://www.dudley.gov.uk/leisure-and-culture/libraries/find-a-library/lye-library-/\">\r\nLye Library\r\n</a>\r\n provides internet access 6 days of the week and access to world class \r\n<a href=\"http://www.dudley.gov.uk/leisure-and-culture/libraries/find-a-library/lye-library-/\">\r\nresearch materials \r\n</a>\r\nMonday to Saturday even in the early evening.\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nVery friendly librarians who work hard to help.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Writing Group</b>\r\n<p>\r\nIf you have an interest in words, enjoy reading and writing (on any level) or would like to write or need help with writing skills why not join our Brand New Writing Group held on Tuesday morning at the Net Cafe.\r\n<br />\r\nFor more details have a word with Keith Stroyde. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Helpers</b>\r\n<p>\r\nWe are looking for volunteer staff to welcome people, make and serve tea and coffee and to help clear up, mornings or afternoons.\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:5em;\">\r\n    <a href=\"googlemaps.php\">\r\n    How to Find us\r\n    </a>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFor more information, please contact\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nKeith Stroyde \r\n<br />\r\n07811 - 343213\r\n<br />\r\n01384 - 894948\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<form action=\"index.php?displaypage=mailform.php\" method=\"post\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"emailrecipient\" \r\nvalue=\"keithstroyde@hotmail.co.uk\">\r\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Email\">\r\n</form>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nSimon Falshaw\r\n<br />\r\n01384 - 423142\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<form action=\"index.php?displaypage=mailform.php\" method=\"post\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"emailrecipient\" \r\nvalue=\"simon.falshaw@christchurchlye.org.uk\">\r\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Email\">\r\n</form>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','LEFT','2012-05-19'),
 (37,'MENU_ITEM',800,100,'NO','Intriguing Quotations','','<h2>\r\n Some things to think about\r\n <br />\r\n <h4>\r\n   but not necessarily to agree with\r\n </h4>\r\n</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n Want to contribute ? email us with your quotes.\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <a href=\\\"javascript:mailPopUp(\\\'Simon.Falshaw@ChristChurchLye.org.uk\\\')\\\">\r\n   Email\r\n </a>\r\n Simon Falshaw\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n If the stars appeared only once a century then men would tremble and believe.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n   Immanuel Kant\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n It is easier for a man to cease to be a man by worshipping as gods things\r\n of his own creation.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n Augustine\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n There is now a overriding imperative to walk more lightly on the earth and \r\n we need to make lifestyle decisions in that light. Making selfish choices\r\n such as flying on holiday or buying a larger car are a symptom of sin.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n   Rt Rev Richard Chartres\r\n   <br />\r\n   Bishop of London\r\n </b>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n The more I study Nature the more I am amazed at the creator.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n  Louis Pasteur\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n Modern humans have been around for only 0.0001% of earth\\\'s history - \r\n almost nothing, really - but even existing for that little while has\r\n required a nearly endless string of good fortune.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n  Bill Bryson in \\\"A Short History of Nearly Everything\\\"\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n Question your own lifestyle, not your neighbour\\\'s.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n  Sharing God\\\'s planet - a Christian version for a sustainable future\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n The average UK citizen produces 9.5 tonnes of CO2 per year. One tonne of CO2\r\n stays in the atmosphere for 100 years.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n  Unattributed\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n The world is charged with the grandeur of God; it will flame out like\r\n shining from shook foil.\r\n <br />\r\n <b>\r\n  Gerald Manley Hopkins\r\n </b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n Want to contribute ? email us with your quotes.\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <a href=\\\"javascript:mailPopUp(\\\'Simon.Falshaw@ChristChurchLye.org.uk\\\')\\\">\r\n   Simon.Falshaw@ChristChurchLye.org.uk\r\n </a>\r\n</p>','LEFT','2008-09-21'),
