 (57,'MENU_ITEM',600,900,'NO','Youth Partners and Communities Together (PACT)','','<br />\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>\r\nYouth Partners and Communities Together (PACT)\r\n</h2>\r\n\r\n<h4>\r\nWhat is PACT ?\r\n</h4>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>\r\nLye and Wollescote Partnership\r\n</h4>\r\n \r\n<p>\r\nResidents in the Lye and Wollescote Partnership area can decide actions about issues affecting their area.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe Lye and Wollescote Partnership works to promote neighbourhood and social renewal in the Lye, Wollescote and Pedmore Fields area.\r\nPACT is open to all residents, business owners and local and community voluntary groups living or working within the Lye and Wollescote and Pedmore Fields area who are interested in regeneration.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIt is supported by the neighbourhood management team and other council representatives. This gives communities the opportunity to influence the actions of service providers and discuss issues needing action. Other partners include local councillors, schools, police, faith organisations, connexions and representatives from Dudley Council\\\'s libraries, housing and education teams.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe group will receive regular reports from Lye youth PACT (Partners and Communities Together) which aims to identify and address issues of community safety and well-being in the area. Lye\\\'s youth PACT is among the first of its kind in the country.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe youth PACT is made up of eight young people aged between 14 and 17 from the Lye and Claycroft Place area. The group came together to work to combat the local negative perception of young people in the area. They\\\'ve been so successful that youth issues are no longer identified as a priority issue at Lye PACT meetings. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nLocal Contacts\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n  <li>\r\n  Keith Stroyde (Youth and Community Worker) \r\n  <br />\r\n  Office 01384 - 894948\r\n  <br />\r\n  Mobile 07811 - 343213\r\n  <br />\r\n\r\n<form action=\\\"index.php?displaypage=mailform.php\\\" method=\\\"post\\\">\r\n<input type=\\\"hidden\\\" name=\\\"emailrecipient\\\" \r\nvalue=\\\"keithstroyde@hotmail.co.uk\\\">\r\n<input type=\\\"submit\\\" value=\\\"Email\\\">\r\n</form>\r\n\r\n  </li>\r\n \r\n  <li>\r\n  Tremaine (Neighbourhood Management) 01384 - 812357\r\n  </li>\r\n\r\n\r\n  <li>\r\n  Kat (Young Persons, Community Safety, Co-ordinator) 01384 - 813278 \r\n  </li>\r\n\r\n  <li>\r\n  PCSO Stuart Preece (Lye Police) 0121 - 626 - 8059\r\n  </li>\r\n\r\n  <li>\r\n  PCSO Sukesh Chohan (Lye Police) 0121 - 626 - 8059\r\n  </li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n','LEFT','2012-02-20'),
